Commands:

	left click			highlight node and print its coordinate

	right click			delete all edges connected to node (and remove highlight)

	shift(hold) + left click	draw lines between nodes

	k (twice to confirm)		delete everything; pressing once freezes screen until
					confirmed (with "k" again) or cancelled (with ESC)

	m				delete highlights

	u				undo

	r				redo

	ESC				exit other modes (cancels deletion, "unstick" shift, ...)

	-				zoom out

	=				zoom in (if current drawing will still fit)



